est political icon worked outdo one another shifting blame for early military failures from lincoln and secretary war edwin stanton mcclellan and fourth that lincoln and stanton deliberately undermined mcclellan because his conciliatory stance towards the south which might have resulted less destructive end the war had richmond fallen result the peninsula campaign proponents this school claim that mcclellan criticized more for his admittedly abrasive personality than for his actual field performance plusieurs caractéristiques géographiques institutions nommées george mcclellan hommage ainsi existe fort mcclellan alabama mcclellan butte forêt nationale mont baker snoqualmie fit voyage lorsqu dirigea étude pacific railroad mcclellan street north bend mcclellan street philadelphie mcclellan road cupertino californie mcclellan elementary school chicago statue équestre bronze honneur mcclellan washington existe statue équestre honneur face philadelphia city hall écrits the mexican war diary george mcclellan william starr myers editor publié titre posthume bayonet exercise school the infantry soldier the use the musket hand hand conflicts traduit manuel écrit français gomard publié tant manual bayonet exercise prepared for the use the army united states the report captain george mcclellan one the officers sent the seat war europe and publié tant the armies europe european cavalry including details the organization the cavalry service among the principal nations europe regulations and instructions for the field service the united states cavalry time war publié tant regulations for the field service cavalry time war mcclellan own story william prime editor